{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, Chang et al.",
    "8 have presented organized evaluation methodologies for LLMs through three essential dimensions: \"what to evaluate,\" \"where to evaluate,\" and \"how to evaluate.\"",
    "Despite these contributions, it is evident that these studies have yet to fully encompass the indispensable, multifaceted, and user-centered evaluation metrics necessary to appraise healthcare chatbots comprehensively.",
    "For example, these studies unable to assess chatbots in terms of empathy, reasoning, up-to-dateness, hallucinations, personalization, relevance, and latency.",
    "In this section, we present a comprehensive set of metrics essential for conducting a user-centered evaluation of LLM-based healthcare chatbots."
  ]
}